{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_01","textHome":"其实我呀，是最近才知道@自己有着时女一族的血统的。@毕竟，连以前应该听外婆提过的妈妈@都没记得这回事，那我不知道也不奇怪了。@然后呀，我现在很激动哦。@因为我终于，得到了能帮助大家的机会！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_17","textHome":"果然刑事或者侦探剧最精彩的地方@就在于每话完结之处！@并非为了让人在意后续，@而是让人感到“哇，看完啦——！”"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_18","textHome":"要说当英雄的梦想，果然还是要解决大事件，@被后世传颂，拍成电影！比如鼠小僧这样的！@……啊，那个是坏人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_19","textHome":"我的鼻子现在很痛，@也就是闻到了案件的气息！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_20","textHome":"我的人生动起来了！@向着英雄加速迈步吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_21","textHome":"完成了使命我便能成为英雄。@但是，成为英雄并不是目的。@改变时女一族才是目的。@现在可不能停下！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_22","textHome":"身负魔法少女的命运，生命可能会很短暂……@但是我们有着在此之上的牢固牵绊！@绝不会输给什么命运！人生苦短呀少女！@我会和静香还有沙绪一起加油的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_23","textHome":"老旧的袜子或者裤子口袋这些，@线一旦开始松掉就会渐渐全部解开。@我们的关系也是那种感觉。@看来是在哪里出现了薄弱的地方呢……@不过我不会放弃。现在的话一定能够修复的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_24","textHome":"乖乖受捕乖乖受捕——！@啊，你在的这个地方正好！@现在你那边传来了案件的气息。@可以的话请协助我哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_25","textHome":"早~上好，起的还挺晚的呢？@啊，不对？可能只是我太早了。@因为今天要从早上开始和妈妈干农活。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_26","textHome":"这可不行，净找些身体好啊饭量大啊的借口。@我可是法官哦！@全权掌管添饭的，添饭的法官哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_02","textHome":"初次见面，我是时女一族的广江千春！@下次有机会的话可以跟我一起巡逻吗？@我呀，很喜欢晃晃悠悠地散步"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_27","textHome":"呼……啊，诶嘿嘿，抱歉啦。@太阳落山的样子会给我一种@心情也低沉下去的感觉。@这可不行，我必须得继续飘在空中发光才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_28","textHome":"好了，睡前做的作业很完美！@毫无疑问会是满分哦！@果然要成为英雄也必须得有头脑才行。@我会不懈努力的哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_29","textHome":"诶嘿嘿，谢谢你今天陪我。@这附近什么都没有，@对我来说的娱乐就是和别人说话了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_30","textHome":"嗅到了！这个气味毫无疑问是魔女……@在她散布诅咒之前，@我广江千春必须做点什么才行！束手就擒吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_31","textHome":"在魔女的结界里见到了另一个我，@那并不是看错了吧……？难到说是幻觉？@唔——还是去确认一下为好么……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_32","textHome":"真是的！大家快住手啊！@为什么，偏要这样打起架来呢？@明明为了除恶而战斗，@和单纯的打架意义是不一样的啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_33","textHome":"好了，要不要去散会儿步呢。@总感觉，就这样呆着心里平静不下来。@啊，可以的话要一起去吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_34","textHome":"总感觉，以教室为场景会让人浮想联翩呢。@会不会突然学校的哪里发生爆炸，@很不得了的人入侵进来之类……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_35","textHome":"我啊，很想试试骑着马飒爽地出镜。@所以最近呢，在负责照顾时女村落的马。@说不定哪天会让我骑在它背上呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_36","textHome":"啊——看到了讨厌的东西……@直觉和嗅觉很灵敏虽然是好事，@但有时也会发现了不知道为好的事情呢。@唉……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_03","textHome":"静香她，真的什么都不知道呢……"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_37","textHome":"要说身边发生的案件的话就是那个！@沙绪！她和我只差一岁对吧！？@但是却可以那么性感的吗！？@是基因的恶作剧！？神的恶作剧！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_38","textHome":"静香她呀，不谙世事这一点很可爱哦！@既没有乘过电车，电视机也只见过@很~旧的像箱子那样的哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_39","textHome":"从最开始我的嗅觉就一直在说哦。@说这个村落有可疑的气息。@不是魔法或者别的什么，@单纯很不可思议地感到有什么要发生……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_40","textHome":"我家一～直以来口口相传的古老文字。@尽管要传下去的理由已经遗失了@，但多亏了我听过这些，@后来起到了很大作用哦"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_41","textHome":"何处何人在呼唤我……@单手耍得十手生辉，凛凛伫立的传奇捕头！@等下、哇——！你看什么呀！？@我还只是在考虑开场白呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":102600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_42","textHome":"好了，乖乖束手就擒吧——！！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_43","textHome":"嗯，心情舒爽了！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_44","textHome":"今天的英雄是我哦！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_45","textHome":"这份胜利，就是改变成规的第一步！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_46","textHome":"因为我的体内也流淌着时女的血！"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_04","textHome":"或许沙绪比起我要更像英雄一些……"}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_63","textHome":"可别因为是十手就瞧不起！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_64","textHome":"这就是让你悔改的，最后一招！！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_65","textHome":"呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_66","textHome":"啊，可能干的太过火了……"}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_05","textHome":"和大家也都处好了关系，@来这一趟真好！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_13","textHome":"来看，我这十手的招式！@这也是和静香认真对练的成果哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_14","textHome":"这就是捕头的绝技！嘿唰唰唰唰！@你已经，逃不掉了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_15","textHome":"想听听我的经历，你可真有闲趣呢。@要听听我找宠物的事吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_16","textHome":"一次我迷路的时候，被派出所的叔叔帮了忙，@从那之后我就一直憧憬着成为英雄啦。@这不算什么很特别的经历对吧？诶嘿……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]}]},"version":3}